query:
INSERT INTO sales (blingOrderId, productId, quantity, unitPrice, totalPrice, orderStatus, saleDate) 
SELECT 
  CONCAT('TEST-', p.id) as blingOrderId,
  p.id as productId,
  FLOOR(1 + RAND() * 10) as quantity,
  FLOOR(p.price * 0.8) as unitPrice,
  FLOOR(p.price * 0.8 * (1 + RAND() * 10)) as totalPrice,
  'Atendido' as orderStatus,
  DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL FLOOR(RAND() * 365) DAY) as saleDate
FROM products p 
WHERE p.isActive = 1 
LIMIT 1000
